  "eligibility":[{"type":"anyOf","sourceText":"计划生育特别扶助分为独生子女死亡家庭和独生子女三级以上残疾家庭两个资格分支，每个分支内部条件均须同时满足。","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-df5bf52711a80242","chunk-231a108c24dfedc1"],"conditions":[{"type":"allOf","sourceText":"独生子女死亡家庭须同时满足北京户籍、规定出生日期、年龄、合法生育或收养、持独生子女父母光荣证且现无存活子女等条件。","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-256d35f059450ee9","chunk-bf7f59e303b03b54","chunk-71c22abcf6a7385c","chunk-080917bc1cf8b4dc","chunk-187b7d4cf25ff894","chunk-4fe3575e4b10969a"],"conditions":[{"type":"condition","field":"hukou","operator":"equals","value":"北京市","sourceText":"本人具有北京市户籍","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-256d35f059450ee9"]},{"type":"condition","field":"birthDate","operator":"greater_than_or_equal","value":"1933-01-01","sourceText":"1933年1月1日以后出生","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-bf7f59e303b03b54"]},{"type":"condition","field":"age","operator":"greater_than_or_equal","value":49,"unit":"周岁","sourceText":"女方年满49周岁；丧偶或离婚单亲家庭男方或女方须年满49周岁","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-71c22abcf6a7385c","chunk-4fe3575e4b10969a"]},{"type":"condition","field":"onlyChildFamilyStatus","operator":"equals","value":"只生育一个子女或合法收养一个子女","sourceText":"只生育一个子女或合法收养一个子女","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-080917bc1cf8b4dc"]},{"type":"condition","field":"hasOnlyChildParentsCertificate","operator":"equals","value":true,"sourceText":"已领取独生子女父母光荣证","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-187b7d4cf25ff894"]},{"type":"condition","field":"hasLivingChild","operator":"equals","value":false,"sourceText":"现无存活子女","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-4fe3575e4b10969a"]}]},{"type":"allOf","sourceText":"独生子女伤残家庭须同时满足北京户籍、女方规定出生日期和年满49周岁、合法生育收养情况、持独生子女父母光荣证，且现存活独生子女为三级以上残疾并持第二代残疾人证。","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-f5c99733f5b8f77f","chunk-3c33cdaa1ad7fe88","chunk-da0f0df2aa138fb1","chunk-f866ee6206f8d0dc","chunk-fed1eeade2f4dcb4","chunk-4ec89cd5abfd316c"],"conditions":[{"type":"condition","field":"hukou","operator":"equals","value":"北京市","sourceText":"本人具有北京市户籍","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-f5c99733f5b8f77f"]},{"type":"condition","field":"femaleBirthDate","operator":"greater_than_or_equal","value":"1933-01-01","sourceText":"女方1933年1月1日以后出生","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-3c33cdaa1ad7fe88"]},{"type":"condition","field":"femaleAge","operator":"greater_than_or_equal","value":49,"unit":"周岁","sourceText":"女方年满49周岁","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-da0f0df2aa138fb1"]},{"type":"condition","field":"onlyChildFamilyStatus","operator":"in","value":["合法生育或收养一个子女","合法生育或收养两个子女现存活一个"],"sourceText":"合法生育（或收养）一个子女或合法生育（或收养）两个子女现存活一个","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-f866ee6206f8d0dc"]},{"type":"condition","field":"hasOnlyChildParentsCertificate","operator":"equals","value":true,"sourceText":"已领取独生子女父母光荣证","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-fed1eeade2f4dcb4"]},{"type":"condition","field":"livingOnlyChildDisabilityLevel","operator":"greater_than_or_equal","value":3,"sourceText":"现存活独生子女为三级以上残疾（含），且持有第二代残疾人证","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-4ec89cd5abfd316c"]}]}]}],
  "applicablePopulation":[{"title":"独生子女死亡或三级以上残疾家庭夫妻","text":"死亡和伤残是两个独立分支，均要求北京户籍、年龄、生育收养历史和独生子女父母光荣证等完整条件。","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-df5bf52711a80242","chunk-231a108c24dfedc1"]}],
  "benefits":[{"title":"现行特别扶助金标准","text":"自2022年7月1日起，独生子女伤残、死亡特别扶助金分别为每人每月740元、900元。","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-c7ab319a39656ffd"]}],
  "materials":[{"title":"资格证明材料","text":"需核验户籍、出生日期、婚姻和生育收养情况、独生子女父母光荣证；伤残分支还需第二代残疾人证，死亡分支需无存活子女相关证明。","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-256d35f059450ee9","chunk-080917bc1cf8b4dc","chunk-187b7d4cf25ff894","chunk-4fe3575e4b10969a","chunk-f5c99733f5b8f77f","chunk-f866ee6206f8d0dc","chunk-fed1eeade2f4dcb4","chunk-4ec89cd5abfd316c"]}],
  "procedures":[{"title":"申请、评议、审核、审批和备案","text":"本人申请，社区居村委会评议，街道乡镇审核，区县人口计生部门审批，市级抽查和备案，并进行年度资格复核。","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-f652ed26626f7a51","chunk-781b6876c142a1fa","chunk-e451d503c0c5e6c1","chunk-dc0a321a068d1d96","chunk-990e207277b23621","chunk-8352b947082c1e51","chunk-b96b9b6974bf3e92","chunk-8200f7254daed0de","chunk-97462d3ae13a15ab","chunk-971957339ea95040"]}],
  "restrictions":[{"title":"再生育或收养后终止","text":"扶助对象再生育或合法收养子女后终止领取扶助金。","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-4fe3575e4b10969a","chunk-4ec89cd5abfd316c"]},{"title":"农村奖励扶助待遇衔接","text":"达到60周岁后按奖励扶助和特别扶助制度中较高标准执行，避免重复按两套标准领取。","sourceChunkIds":["chunk-a66ccc78679c0023","chunk-8a2946be920bea50"]}],
  "unresolvedQuestions":["现行经办部门名称、申请表和材料清单是否更新","独生子女父母光荣证遗失等特殊情况的当前认定口径","伤残等级和证件当前是否有效"],
  "plainLanguage":{"officialInterpretationSourceIds":[],"humanVerified":"计划生育特别扶助有两条分支：独生子女死亡家庭和独生子女三级以上残疾家庭。两条都不是只看孩子的状态，还必须同时核对北京户籍、出生和年龄、生育或收养历史、独生子女父母光荣证等条件。本人申请后还要经过社区评议、街乡审核和区级审批；以后再生育或合法收养子女会停止领取。"},"extractedAt":"2026-07-11","verifiedAt":"2026-07-11"
}
